{"tid":2449592,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"38歲男督察　確診前三日　曾打科興疫苗第一針","createTime":"2021-03-16T20:53:59.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-17T05:24:05.000Z","uid":261647,"like":13,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"2b87a4e50083672276287ccc9896d61c9933f80d","tid":2449592,"uid":261647,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-16T20:53:59.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/hkcnews/posts/1407470842929654\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fhkcnews%2Fposts%2F1407470842929654&d=JW7tglSI9GVP0ZLjrScixe6cow1LS9WQT%2BeJ8I%2F17x8%3D&h=7e27e905\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/hkcnews/posts/1407470842929654</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/1UGTnyP.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F1UGTnyP.jpg&h=3d56d72a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n作者：眾新聞<br />\n<br />\n【消息：男督察確診前三日　曾打科興疫苗第一針】<br />\n<br />\n眾新聞得悉，早前確診的一名38歲男督察，在確診前三日曾經接種科興疫苗第一針，或會成為香港首宗注射疫苗後的確診個案。<br />\n<br />\n警方周一（15日）表示，一名刑事部男督察初步確診。根據警方說法，當時是因為其家人較早前懷疑接觸確診者，所以主動測試並呈陽性反應。警方指，該男警沒有與公眾接觸，並在3月12日最後上班。據悉，該男警是於3月12日接種科興疫苗，無論是警方的新聞公布或衞生署記者會，都無提及該男警曾經接種疫苗。眾新聞正向警方及衞生署查詢。<br />\n<br />\n科興及BioNTech均需接種兩劑疫苗。政府專家顧問、中大呼吸系統科講座教授許樹昌指，接種了第一劑疫苗後仍然會有機會受感染，接種者需要在接種疫苗後兩周，抗體才會達至足夠的保護水平，舉例在BioNTech第三期臨床數據中，在接種第一劑疫苗後數天，疫苗有效率為82%，但在接種第二劑前數天會跌至52%；在接種第二劑後，疫苗有效率才會回升至95%。"},{"pid":"7ea4c23dad6815a09da32253d1a420289bf95afa","tid":2449592,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-17T04:17:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e7ff6acd6551d772db10c3c4d2a302af6a013e10","tid":2449592,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-17T04:19:16.000Z","msg":"同飲符水一樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/OL64wHH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FOL64wHH.jpg&h=8da49253&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"cd91724dbe4bf35350f6f9d0f51afb7213bd15a8","tid":2449592,"uid":92479,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-17T05:01:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ba838376f8d52f9e5a53c79d5f9a3f68c9fb02f7","tid":2449592,"uid":44562,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-17T05:02:21.000Z","msg":"終於等到 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"be1cc6b46b4b13798c29e6473402101854fbbdb2","tid":2449592,"uid":66898,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-17T05:14:39.000Z","msg":"大佬呀 人地打科興 你拎BioNTech 黎做例子<br />\n2樣技術都唔撚同, 完係冇關係既野 只係目的一樣都可以拉埋一齊講<br />\n重有 做咩唔拎科興第3期數據解畫呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cb2daffdc6565c2a1caf946eb3c673034f6a1c6b","tid":2449592,"uid":121409,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-17T05:14:54.000Z","msg":"又拖国家後腿<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7fa55a31fb6c414e369eb8cf987aca713365ba0c","tid":2449592,"uid":273218,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-17T05:24:05.000Z","msg":"打科興既國家<br />\n疫情數字居高不下"}]}